IPCM0EL: calculated by the function combine_tables_varying_in_one_sheet_as by CC and JN from PRIMAPCheck info_per_country.csv for further information. For countries without emissions provided in the NDC but with inclLU emissions provided, the exclLU emissions were calculated based on NDC_inclLU minus {table_onlyLU.tablename}. For countries without emissions provided in the NDC the KYOTOGHG_IPCM0EL_TOTAL_NET_SSP5BLREMMPFILLED_PMSSPBIE values are used.
